{"tid":2375402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"調查指只有17%港人對置業感興趣","createTime":"2021-01-22T04:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T11:36:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9873563daf52558a366224cd4421158468a27f","tid":2375402,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pZpelayxxnvNobX9KAZkoA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMDAuOA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/nktAdZ3_rPD.Ne1Hjfd.aw--~B/aD02ODg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/thesun.hk.com/26027de1802c287ed38d15796c33d7d8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpZpelayxxnvNobX9KAZkoA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMDAuOA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnktAdZ3_rPD.Ne1Hjfd.aw--~B%2FaD02ODg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F26027de1802c287ed38d15796c33d7d8&h=08f29c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n花旗銀行發表去年第四季市民置業意向調查，結果顯示有17%受訪者表示有興趣入市，與去年第三季持平，同時預期未來樓價平穩的比例升至43%，按季多9個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇淡樓價佔比降至36%<br />\n<br />\n該調查於去年12月以隨機抽樣電話訪問形式，訪問逾500名本港市民。當中認為現時屬好或極好置業時機的受訪者佔8%，按季輕微回落約兩個百分點，但仍比疫情前8年為高。另外，按調查結果推算，去年第四季有約32.5萬人於11月內有參觀樓盤，數字雖比同年第三季近40萬人回落，但人數比2019年同期仍高約35%。<br />\n<br />\n展望未來樓價，估計未來樓價下跌的受訪者比例，由去年第三季約43%，下調至上一季的36%，減少達7個百分點。該行零售銀行業務主管李貴莊表示，市民逐漸適應疫情的周期性變化，對樓價的展望亦漸趨平穩，隨着今年經濟復甦可期，累積的置業需求有望釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/調查-港人置業意欲未減-214500899.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E6%84%8F%E6%AC%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%B8%9B-214500899.html&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=47e3f949\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/調查-港人置業意欲未減-214500899.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3628d65125b807cd6656fb156c5b0dcd1f8897d","tid":2375402,"uid":149844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"無錢點會有興趣買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5cf3136f4eb71df5f56457979dcbc5804c1c52","tid":2375402,"uid":228955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"成個地方有問題點會仲想喺呢個地方長住"},{"pid":"5f06e5e18a42085ab9712de6b1f3d9a55c81d44f","tid":2375402,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"仲諗住買樓嘅係因為想博佢升值 花無百日紅點可能無止境咁升"},{"pid":"8768510e2e49eb6d37f15062975c87776bbaab23","tid":2375402,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"可能果17% 既人可以炒起哂全港既樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓市gogogo"},{"pid":"e4a6dad0aa79f5f6deb23ea8ee0cacb932553dbc","tid":2375402,"uid":48500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"有錢即刻仆去買再po曬全部平台曬"},{"pid":"35702f6c203f8bc7a4f6912c46ed9a28f91b113b","tid":2375402,"uid":269137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"有錢我都搬去安全國家啦<br />\n唔通等被共產咩"},{"pid":"3c784a10e9537d67c44dddc73e84b9efe631dfa2","tid":2375402,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係同一班人炒"},{"pid":"f555cf42035d5f9a103e1f5fdb7c706e4fefd33e","tid":2375402,"uid":222392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"有得揀，先至係老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8667d4a4231680ec69c484504b43488fca9f70e9","tid":2375402,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8768510e2e49eb6d37f15062975c87776bbaab23","tid":2375402,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"可能果17% 既人可以炒起哂全港既樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓市gogogo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04: